/*+++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++
+                                                                                                             +
+ Given an element a of an axial Algebra A, find the matrix of ad_a. The element a must really be axial.      +
+													      +
++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++===+++*/

AdMat:=function(a)
A:=Parent(a); F:=BaseField(A);
return Matrix(F,[Eltseq(a*A.i):i in [1..Dimension(A)]]);
end function;
